  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Study Comparing AVP-786 With AVP-923</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Single-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Double-dummy, 2-way Crossover Study Comparing AVP-786 With AVP-923</official_title>
  <sponsors>
