  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare pharmacokinetics (PK) of AVP-786 (deuterated [d6] dextromethorphan hydrobromide
      [d6-DM]/quinidine sulfate [Q]) to AVP-923 (dextromethorphan hydrobromide [DM]/Q) at steady
      state.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
